---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section style="padding: 2rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">❓ Questions</h1>
    
    <details style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <summary><strong>Is TubeSEO free?</strong></summary>
      <p>Yes! TubeSEO v1.0 is completely free to download and use.</p>
    </details>

    <details style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <summary><strong>Does TubeSEO work on macOS or Linux?</strong></summary>
      <p>No. TubeSEO is currently Windows-only. Support for other platforms may come in the future.</p>
    </details>

    <details style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <summary><strong>How do I uninstall TubeSEO?</strong></summary>
      <p>Open Windows Settings → Apps → Find "TubeSEO" → Click Uninstall.</p>
    </details>

    <details style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <summary><strong>Is TubeSEO safe?</strong></summary>
      <p>Yes. TubeSEO is safe to install and use. It runs locally and does not collect any data.</p>
    </details>

    <details style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
      <summary><strong>Will there be updates?</strong></summary>
      <p>Yes. TubeSEO v1.1 and beyond will include new features and improvements.</p>
    </details>

  </section>
</Layout>
